WEBVTT

00:00:01.592 --> 00:00:04.270
[Rebeka Njuberger Goldstajn]

00:00:04.270 --> 00:00:06.349
[Stiven Pinker]

00:00:06.349 --> 00:00:09.626
["Dalekosežnost razuma"]

00:00:11.348 --> 00:00:14.641
Taksista: Dvadeset dva dolara.
Stiven Pinker: Okej.

00:00:17.857 --> 00:00:21.975
Rebeka Njuberger Goldstajn: Čini se
da se teško vreme nadvilo nad razumom:

00:00:21.975 --> 00:00:25.310
pop kultura pronalazi
nove dubine gluposti,

00:00:25.310 --> 00:00:27.776
a politički diskurs je postao trka

00:00:27.776 --> 00:00:30.791
do dna.